dc_title_s: Atlantic Ocean, Haiti--Dominican Republic, Fort Liberté and Manzanillo (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by hachures. "From U.S. Navy surveys and a U.S. chart to 1985." "Copyright 1995 by the U.S. Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Inset: Manzanillo. Scale 1:20,000. Includes compilation diagram. Map no.26145 This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
